  <notes>
- initial version for SDL2, rewrite from scratch providing procedural style and object oriented style
- implemented classes:
  SDL_Color
  SDL_cond
  SDL_Cursor
  SDL_DisplayMode
  SDL_GLContext
  SDL_MessageBoxButtonData
  SDL_MessageBoxColor
  SDL_MessageBoxData
  SDL_mutex
  SDL_Palette
  SDL_PixelFormat
  SDL_Pixels (PHP specific)
  SDL_Point
  SDL_Rect
  SDL_RWops
  SDL_sem
  SDL_Surface
  SDL_Window
  SDL_WindowShapeMode
  </notes>
